race.comment: BAR JESTER (1) led and won the Clan O'Sullivan in impressive fashion, with the form from behind her being franked in recent times. The inside draw should see him right on the pace once again for Keatings and they meet at level weights once again. Can repeat the dose. MUSIC TIME (3) couldn't get by BAR JESTER first-up before bolting in here a fortnight ago. Drawing out there looked a big key to his win and he draws away from the rail again today for Boudvillain. Will be spotting BAR JESTER a start but should be winding up late. SOMERFORD (9) has shown promising signs at the trials and is not to be discounted on debut. PAULINE'S DREAM (8) turned in a sneaky good trial behind Spread The Love coming into this and represents some value.
